# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# APPOINTMENTS - ADMIN CREATE AUTHORIZATION CHECKS
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Tests that non-admin mechanics cannot use POST /api/customers/{id}/appointments.
# Run in sequence: login as non-admin, attempt create (403), logout, retry (401).

@AutoService_ApiService_HostAddress = {{$processEnv AutoService_ApiService_HostAddress}}
@NonAdminEmail = {{$processEnv ARSM_TEST_MECHANIC_EMAIL}}
@NonAdminPassword = {{$processEnv ARSM_TEST_MECHANIC_PASSWORD}}
@CustomerId = 1
@VehicleId = 1


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### [Setup][Appointments] Login as non-admin mechanic
POST {{AutoService_ApiService_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{NonAdminEmail}}",
  "password": "{{NonAdminPassword}}"
}

###

### [Negative][Appointments] Non-admin mechanic cannot create appointment for customer (403 expected)
# POST /api/customers/{customerId}/appointments requires AdminOnly policy.
POST {{AutoService_ApiService_HostAddress}}/api/customers/{{CustomerId}}/appointments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vehicleId": {{VehicleId}},
  "scheduledDate": "2026-04-30T10:00:00",
  "dueDateTime": "2026-05-01T10:00:00",
  "taskDescription": "Non-admin create attempt — should be rejected with 403",
  "mechanicIds": [1]
}

###

### [Setup][Appointments] Logout non-admin session
POST {{AutoService_ApiService_HostAddress}}/api/auth/logout

###

### [Negative][Appointments] Unauthenticated admin create appointment for customer (401 expected)
# Confirms the endpoint is protected even with no session at all.
POST {{AutoService_ApiService_HostAddress}}/api/customers/{{CustomerId}}/appointments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vehicleId": {{VehicleId}},
  "scheduledDate": "2026-04-30T10:00:00",
  "dueDateTime": "2026-05-01T10:00:00",
  "taskDescription": "Unauthenticated admin create — should be rejected with 401",
  "mechanicIds": [1]
}
